getAuctionByToken(address,uint256).details: returns auction id by token address and token id

getCurrentBuyer(uint256).details: returns current highest bidder for an auction

getMinimalNextBid(uint256).details: returns the minimal amount of the next bid (without fees)

owner().details: Returns the address of the current owner.

putBid(uint256,(uint256,bytes4,bytes)).details: put a bid and return locked assets for the last bid

putBidWrapper(uint256).details: function to call from wrapper to put bid

renounceOwnership().details: Leaves the contract without owner. It will not be possible to call `onlyOwner` functions anymore. Can only be called by the current owner. NOTE: Renouncing ownership will leave the contract without an owner, thereby removing any functionality that is only available to the owner.

startAuction(((bytes4,bytes),uint256),(b.details: creates an auction and locks sell asset

supportsInterface(bytes4).details: See {IERC165-supportsInterface}. Time complexity O(1), guaranteed to always use less than 30 000 gas.

transferOwnership(address).details: Transfers ownership of the contract to a new account (`newOwner`). Can only be called by the current owner.

EXTENSION_DURATION.details: minimal auction duration and also the time for that auction is extended when it's about to end (endTime - now < EXTENSION_DURATION)

auctions.details: mapping to store data of auctions for auctionId
